Major League Baseball to Take Over Operations of Dodgers, Selig Says

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-04-20T21:09:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/major-league-baseball-to-take-over-operations-of-dodgers-selig-says.html
Major League Baseball  will appoint
someone to oversee business and day-to-day operations of the  Los
Angeles Dodgers , Commissioner Bud Selig said in a statement.  Selig said he has “deep concerns” over the finances and
day-to-day operations of the club.  To contact the reporter on this story:
